    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on how those arguments—especially the Mill idea—could be used to argue that even things like anti-misinformation laws or content moderation requirements are inherently unconstitutional/unjust? I want to show that once the gov starts deciding what's \"true,\" it's game over for liberty.",
